{"word":"G3660 - ὀμνύω - omnýō - om-noo'-o - Swear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀμνύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">omnýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">om-noo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Swear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சத்தியம் பண்ணு, ஆணையிடு"},{"paragraph":"to swear, to vow, to make an oath"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a primary but obsolete word, <b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03C9;</b> <b>omo&#x0304;</b>, for which another prolonged form (<b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>omoo&#x0304;</b>  <i>om-o'-o</i>) is used in certain tenses. To <i>swear</i>, that is, <i>take</i> (or <i>declare on</i>) <i>oath:</i> - swear.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}